cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it deals with natural language processing and dependency parsing. The use of LSTM recurrent neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the incorporation of character-based encodings could also make it relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.CV (Computer Vision) sub-categories.
